[node name="InspectableInteraction" parent="." unique_id=400000004 instance=ExtResource("2_a4uc4")]
content = "[center][b]Final Notes[/b][/center]

Shelter before sunset.
Water before shelter.
Fire before water.

That's the order. Took me two days to learn it properly.

[color=#8B4513]If you're reading this — you found all three pages. You know the camp well enough now.[/color]

Trust your training. Trust the guide.

[i]Good luck, Scout.[/i]"
